front.title: •Quietly Observing (V)
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Aurra, Bossk, and Cad are destiny +2. Once per game, may reveal up to two unique (•) aliens from hand and/or Reserve Deck (reshuffle); for remainder of game, those cards are assassins and Black Sun agents. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: On her assignment to kill Sharad Hett, Aurra used her patience and cunning to help track down the Jedi Master.
